4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience, aiming to cultivate expertise in cybersecurity. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring 3 live online classes each week, and accommodates up to 18 students per class. Participants will build a strong foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, while developing skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The bootcamp also covers risk management and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop